{"tid":266780,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[日本自駕保險] ToCoo租車網好撚on9 有無巴打指點吓？","createTime":"2017-06-01T17:41:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-03T18:33:18.000Z","uid":14216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bcade7ca88e5c5a71d99c5fbd6712f488e269a43","tid":266780,"uid":14216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T17:41:37.000Z","msg":"是咁的 我嚟緊會同屋企人去日本關東自駕 <br />\n已有兩次自駕經驗 之前喺Toyota同埋經tabirai向times租都好順利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為我地想坐得舒服少少 所以今次只會揀nissan elgrand或者toyota alphard<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇過要行嘅高速後發現用tocoo expressway pass會抵啲，所以決定經佢地租，但問題就來了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1) 經tocoo租NISSAN：<br />\n</span>一定要加T.A.S.（ToCoo Additional Support）～NOC，但係佢話：注意、Nippon Rental Car的預約不可享有N.O.C.的補助。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 逼你加錢但又唔包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">2)  經tocoo向NIPPON Rent-A-Car租toyota alphard：<br />\n</span>包 T.R.S.（ToCoo Roadsaide Support），姐係唔包NOC<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=